{"tid":112390,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【一月新番】Hand Shakers 集中討論","createTime":"2017-02-08T06:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T01:07:30.000Z","uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76d8d52c2cfb0a42e759c3a569e6204dcfe6c984","tid":112390,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/uxv5vsxon/Hand_Shakers_key.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fuxv5vsxon%2FHand_Shakers_key.jpg&h=bbd23209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n■ STORY<br />\n《Hand Shakers》指的是藉由手牽著手、靠從深層的心理產生的武器 Nimrod 來互相戰鬥的人們。 <br />\n為了實現自己的「願望」、與神見面、 不將''神''給殺死...等眾多的<br />\nHand Shakers 們為了邁向那頂點而彼此競爭著。 <br />\n在那盡頭等待著的將會是靠這雙手來守護。<br />\n<br />\n■ STAFF <br />\n原作：GoHands<br />\n音樂：GOON TRAX<br />\n動畫製作：GoHands<br />\n<br />\n■ CAST<br />\n手綱：齊藤壯馬<br />\n小依：諸星堇<br />\n牧原：森久保祥太郎<br />\n莉莉：茅野愛衣<br />\n勝：村瀨步<br />\n千鶴：上坂堇<br />\n疾風：石川界人<br />\n小玉：小松未可子<br />\n響：杉田智和<br />\n布雷克：福山潤<br />\n拜因德：日笠陽子<br />\n<br />\n■ INFO<br />\n<a href=\"http://project-hs.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproject-hs.net&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=2159ced4\" target=\"_blank\">http://project-hs.net</a><br />\n<br />\n逢星期二晚 23:30 (香港時間)<br />\n<a href=\"http://mov3.co/tokyomx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmov3.co%2Ftokyomx%2F&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=63bdc9b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://mov3.co/tokyomx/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.zhanqi.tv/meizhi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhanqi.tv%2Fmeizhi&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e22e5d50\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.zhanqi.tv/meizhi</a>"},{"pid":"3954c3015034328daad8ac0288e97df5b6dea82d","tid":112390,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ebb.io/anime/48x69\" data-sr-url=